    <para id="id1167320079421"><emphasis effect="italics">This velocity is not thermal velocity but velocity resulting from Pauli’s Exclusion Principle which essentially is the result of the ferm-ionic nature of electrons. </emphasis>Electrons tend to repel one another when confined in a small Cartesian Space. Electrons are claustrophobic. </para>
